name: Still Life 16.1
description:
Fizz Pop (b.1974)  
August 2021 
12000 x 9600 pixels 

  This digital painting is a visual representation of key NFT’s minted by the end of August 2021. The Landscape collection minted on Foundation is represented by eleven tulips. The Still Life collection on Hic et Nunc is represented by eighteen stalks of wheat. Flower 01, the first NFT sold of Rarible & Flower 35.0, minted on Kalamint, are represented by the tulip & wheat resting at the foot of the vase.
